00:32:15,876 --> 00:32:18,271
two dark figures in some kind of mass exodus.

521
00:32:19,706 --> 00:32:22,450
I don't know. I just write what comes to me, you know?

522
00:32:22,475 --> 00:32:26,581
So, look, I got to stay. One of my students is going up, and I promised I'd listen.

523
00:32:26,587 --> 00:32:27,733
So I'll see you later?

524
00:32:27,935 --> 00:32:28,882
- All right.
- Ok.

525
00:32:34,077 --> 00:32:35,371
I think he's a sensitive.

526
00:32:36,106 --> 00:32:37,283
- What?
- A sensitive.

527
00:32:38,028 --> 00:32:41,223
My grandma told me about them. I've only met one or two before.

528
00:32:41,775 --> 00:32:44,761
They're people that are somehow in tune with the larger picture.

529
00:32:44,776 --> 00:32:47,073
And they get a feeling about something before

