534
00:32:56,236 --> 00:32:59,251
The day I got into my accident, there was a ghost family in the road,

535
00:32:59,258 --> 00:33:03,500
and I stopped to try and help them, but they got whisked away just like Ashton said.

536
00:33:03,515 --> 00:33:06,590
How can he see them in a dream and I can't find Brian to save my life.

537
00:33:06,605 --> 00:33:07,750
I mean, it's not fair.

538
00:33:08,876 --> 00:33:11,620
I just wish that my grandmother was here so I could...

539
00:33:14,986 --> 00:33:15,933
What?

540
00:33:16,376 --> 00:33:18,822
I know who I'm gonna have to talk to about this.

541
00:33:21,986 --> 00:33:23,033
Mmm, it's delicious.

542
00:33:23,876 --> 00:33:25,423
I don't know. For some reason,

