00:33:34,805 --> 00:33:35,750
I wonder.

547
00:33:37,327 --> 00:33:39,662
I know that you don't like it when I bring up the spirit world...

548
00:33:39,668 --> 00:33:41,220
haven't seen a one.

549
00:33:42,115 --> 00:33:43,322
Haven't heard a thing.

550
00:33:43,918 --> 00:33:45,220
- Nothing?
- No.

551
00:33:46,055 --> 00:33:48,120
- Blessed silence.
- Interesting.

552
00:33:49,377 --> 00:33:51,321
I haven't either for about a week now.

553
00:33:51,586 --> 00:33:52,532
Really?

554
00:33:53,135 --> 00:33:55,941
Oh, this is wonderful. You must be so happy.

555
00:33:56,627 --> 00:33:58,172
No, mom, I'm not.

556
00:34:00,006 --> 00:34:01,823
I know, I know.

557
00:34:02,496 --> 00:34:03,830
You embrace your gift.

558
00:34:04,956 --> 00:34:08,140
Melinda, you can say this till the cows come home,

559
00:34:09,305 --> 00:34:11,131
but aren't you just a little bit relieved?

560
00:34:11,138 --> 00:34:12,080
No.

561
00:34:13,975 --> 00:34:14,923
Maybe it's like...

562
00:34:15,466 --> 00:34:17,561
allergies, you know? You grow out of it.

563
00:34:18,307 --> 00:34:20,201
You always had migraines, right?

564
00:34:21,126 --> 00:34:24,173
Because you were trying to suppress the visions, the sounds.

565
00:34:24,278 --> 00:34:25,853
But your headaches are gone now.

566
00:34:25,856 --> 00:34:27,041
What if there aren't any

567
00:34:27,045 --> 00:34:31,142
visions or sounds to suppress? What if the spirits themselves have just vanished?

568
00:34:31,848 --> 00:34:32,792
Couldn't be.

569
00:34:33,287 --> 00:34:37,061
They're all around us, always. That is what is so annoying about them.

570
00:34:37,548 --> 00:34:38,942
Do you really feel annoyed,

571
00:34:39,286 --> 00:34:42,080
mom? Because to me you've never seemed so lighthearted.

572
00:34:42,185 --> 00:34:46,081
Does it really seem likely that we would both lose our gift at the same time?

573
00:34:46,206 --> 00:34:47,402
So what are you saying?

574
00:34:48,576 --> 00:34:50,022
They've gone somewhere else?

575
00:34:51,465 --> 00:34:53,031
I don't know. Maybe. Yeah.

576
00:34:53,665 --> 00:34:54,610
For good?

577
00:34:56,495 --> 00:34:57,443
I hope not.

578
00:35:06,576 --> 00:35:07,673
Ok, this is all good.

579
00:35:08,128 --> 00:35:11,003
But I don't want you to overdo it just 'cause you feel good.

580
00:35:11,006 --> 00:35:13,862
Let's remember you suffered a head trauma, so the slightest symptom

581
00:35:13,865 --> 00:35:15,392
